'''Delat Personal Electronics''' was a consumer goods manufacturing corporation. The company specialized in [[Datapad/Legends|datapads]] and [[Holoprojector/Legends|holoprojectors]]. It was headquartered on [[Elrood/Legends|Elrood]] in the [[Elrood sector/Legends|Elrood sector]] and had offices located in the [[Elrood Bazaar]].

